picturecard.title: Hi, I'm Botond!
picturecard.textHighlighted: I like the outdoors, the sunshine, listening to prog rock and of course, above all else I like computer stuff.
picturecard.text: From childhood Lego sets, through high school game jams and university web projects, to my current work with algorithmics and AI, I've always enjoyed building things and solving problems!
